{"tid":992714,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"曾批中國施政 澳籍華裔作家失蹤","createTime":"2019-01-23T11:16:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-23T12:43:49.000Z","uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"733aac98c2ecd93a32784736c66846daa9f422e9","tid":992714,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T11:16:57.000Z","msg":"【曾批中國施政 澳籍華裔作家】<br />\n【楊恒均據報於中國失蹤】<br />\n<br />\n53 歲的華裔澳洲籍作家楊恒均，據報上周由美國飛到中國後失蹤。<br />\n<br />\n楊恒均的朋友表示，楊恒均上星期跟太太及小朋友，由美國紐約飛到廣州，之後失去聯絡，懷疑楊恒均被中國國安部人員扣留在北京。<br />\n<br />\n澳洲當局表示，正尋求一名澳洲公民在中國報稱失蹤的資料。<br />\n<br />\n楊恒均曾是中國外交人員，其後入籍澳洲，近年居於美國。<br />\n<br />\n楊恒均是著名作家和時事評論家，多次批評中國政府施政。<br />\n<br />\n#有線新聞　#華裔　#icablenews　#hknews　#cablenews　#newsdaily　#news　#作家　#楊恒均　#中國　#失蹤<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/313223199302751/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ficablenews%2Fvideos%2F313223199302751%2F&d=aJoDg7%2FdIljMrna1Ylq5yP755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=d05a2cc8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/313223199302751/</a>"},{"pid":"65fb07e8ff43fbf6f4a67d5ac6e092059a38e2f4","tid":992714,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T11:52:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78848a569679803123e30720a31b68d20527e4f7","tid":992714,"uid":158888,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T12:41:24.000Z","msg":"繼續扣留多啲人<br />\nN國聯軍指日可待<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bcf3ba9e6a5392f48bccad3a2e67ab4b31afee2","tid":992714,"uid":221773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"78848a569679803123e30720a31b68d20527e4f7","tid":992714,"uid":158888,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T12:41:24.000Z","msg":"繼續扣留多啲人<br />\nN國聯軍指日可待<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T12:43:49.000